#  Built frontend output (Vite builds into the .NET app)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# This folder is generated by `npm run build`. Ignoring it keeps compiled
# JS/CSS out of git — a fresh clone runs `npm run build` to regenerate it.
# If you'd rather commit a static UI (e.g. the no-build index.html), delete
# this line and commit wwwroot manually.
CodeReviewAssistant/wwwroot/

